核心能力 Competence
■ 應用電漿、天文與太空理論和模擬等專業知識解決問題的能力
融通專業知識 The ability to apply professional knowledge of plasma, astrophysical and space theory and simulation to derive solutions to problems
Professional knowledge integration and application□ 具備設計並執行科學實驗，分析與解釋實驗結果的能力
培養研究創新能力 The ability to plan and perform scientific experiments, to analyze and explain experimental results
Creativity■ 具備足夠之外文能力
國際化能力 Foreign language proficiency
The ability to engage in an international context□ 具備在團隊中達成有效溝通、合作領導之能力
培養領袖人才 Leadership ability to achieve effective communication and cooperation
Leadership cultivation■ 瞭解太空、天文與電漿科學研究之進展及相關工程技術，具備跨領域學習之能力
培養跨領域能力 The ability to understand the development of scientific and engineering technology of space, astrophysical and plasma science researches and engage in interdisciplinary study
Interdisciplinary study ability□ 具備科學數據判讀與分析之能力
培養跨領域能力 The ability to interpret and analyze scientific data
Interdisciplinary study ability 

課程概述 Course Description
       To introduce concepts of multi scale physics of plasma-wave systems. 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Understand kinetic equationUnderstand the method to solve kinetic equationUnderstand how to use kinetic equation to describe physics phenomenon 

